  <p>By using SpaceHub India you agree to these terms. Please read them carefully.</p>

  <h5 class="fw-semibold mt-4">1. Platform Role</h5>
  <p>SpaceHub is a marketplace connecting hosts and guests. We are not a party to the rental agreement between hosts and guests.</p>

  <h5 class="fw-semibold mt-4">2. Booking & Payments</h5>
  <p>Bookings are confirmed only after payment is completed. Payments are processed by Razorpay or Stripe. SpaceHub collects a 15% service fee from each booking.</p>

  <h5 class="fw-semibold mt-4">3. Cancellations</h5>
  <p>Guests may cancel bookings up to 24 hours before the start time for a full refund. Cancellations within 24 hours are non-refundable.</p>

  <h5 class="fw-semibold mt-4">4. Host Responsibilities</h5>
  <p>Hosts must ensure listings are accurate and spaces are available as described. Hosts are responsible for compliance with local laws and regulations.</p>

