  <p>Users are responsible for content they submit. SpaceHub reserves the right to remove listings or reviews that violate our community guidelines.</p>

  <h5 class="fw-semibold mt-4">6. Limitation of Liability</h5>
  <p>SpaceHub is not liable for damages arising from the use of listed spaces. Use the platform at your own risk.</p>

  <h5 class="fw-semibold mt-4">7. Governing Law</h5>
  <p>These terms are governed by the laws of India. Disputes shall be resolved in the courts of Mumbai, Maharashtra.</p>

  <p class="mt-4 text-muted small">Questions? Email legal@spacehub.in</p>
